==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Blackcock
<hw>Black"cock`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>The male of the European black grouse (<spn>Tetrao tetrix</spn>,
Linn.); -- so called by sportsmen. The female is called <xex>gray
hen</xex>. See <er>Heath grouse</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Black comedy</ent>⟦br⟧
